sources.title: Red Ryder | Stagecoach to Denver (Western, 1946) Allan Lane, Robert Blake | Full Length Movie
sources.description:
RIDE THE OUTLAWS' HIGHWAY! Lambert has the stagecoach wrecked killing the Commissioner so his phony replacement can alter the land survey. When Red Ryder exposes the survey hoax, Lambert has his stooge Sheriff put Red in jail.

Director: R.G. Springsteen
Writers: Earle Snell , Fred Harman 
Stars: Allan Lane, Robert Blake, Martha Wentworth
Genres: Classics, Western
